<view class="currency-settings-container data-v-fc6c42f6"><view class="header data-v-fc6c42f6"><text class="title data-v-fc6c42f6">币种汇率设置</text><text class="subtitle data-v-fc6c42f6">设置各币种兑人民币的汇率</text></view><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="loading-section data-v-fc6c42f6"><text class="loading-text data-v-fc6c42f6">加载中...</text></view><view wx:elif="{{b}}" class="currency-list data-v-fc6c42f6"><view wx:for="{{c}}" wx:for-item="rate" wx:key="k" class="{{['currency-item', 'data-v-fc6c42f6', rate.l && 'disabled']}}"><view class="currency-info data-v-fc6c42f6"><view class="currency-header data-v-fc6c42f6"><text class="currency-symbol data-v-fc6c42f6">{{rate.a}}</text><text class="currency-name data-v-fc6c42f6">{{rate.b}}</text><text class="currency-code data-v-fc6c42f6">{{rate.c}}</text></view><view class="rate-row data-v-fc6c42f6"><text class="rate-label data-v-fc6c42f6">1 {{rate.d}} =</text><input type="digit" class="rate-input data-v-fc6c42f6" value="{{rate.e}}" disabled="{{rate.f}}" bindblur="{{rate.g}}" placeholder="请输入汇率"/><text class="rate-unit data-v-fc6c42f6">CNY</text></view></view><view class="currency-toggle data-v-fc6c42f6"><switch class="data-v-fc6c42f6" checked="{{rate.h}}" disabled="{{rate.i}}" bindchange="{{rate.j}}" color="#F7B84D"/></view></view></view><view class="save-section data-v-fc6c42f6"><button class="save-btn data-v-fc6c42f6" loading="{{d}}" bindtap="{{e}}"> 保存设置 </button></view><view class="tips-section data-v-fc6c42f6"><text class="tips-title data-v-fc6c42f6">说明</text><text class="tips-item data-v-fc6c42f6">• 汇率表示 1 单位外币兑换的人民币金额</text><text class="tips-item data-v-fc6c42f6">• 人民币汇率固定为 1，无法修改</text><text class="tips-item data-v-fc6c42f6">• 关闭的币种将不会在记账时显示</text><text class="tips-item data-v-fc6c42f6">• 默认汇率仅供参考，请根据实际情况调整</text></view></view>